branchCategory.name: 90-ZSE50F, High Precision Digital Pressure Switch for Compound Pressure
branchCategory.description: <p>High precision digital pressure switch series 90-ZSE50 is a standard thread type for compound pressure.  90-ZSE50 is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. 90-ZSE50 is used for a wide range of fluids. The stainless steel diaphragm prevents direct contact between sensor and measured fluid.  Sensor and fittings are electro-beam welded.  </p>
